@node Beschreibung "description of the program"

                            Artefact-Generator

the program should works on all computersystems like Amiga.
it is shell-oriented, it means, all datainputs are done in the shell.
the output can be chosen by TeX or ASCII. its done by the option -t.
the TeX or ASCII-file includes a full description with .tex or .doc.

options :
 -l   language       possible:   e(english) und g(german)
                     standard:   g
 -s   filename       Standard:   artefakt
 -t   outputformat   possible:   TeX/TEX/Tex/tex or ASCII/Ascii/ascii
                     standard:   TeX

